data.description:
AGENT-OWNER. Two move-in ready houses are sitting on 1,835 acres land with NO restrictions. Fully fenced!
It's a hidden gem with plenty of trees, lots of privacy and plenty of space to park your RVs,
boats and 4wheelers. Very low property tax rate! UNIT A: 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bath, new windows Andersen, Roof 2015, all new appliances, fresh paint, granite countertops, back porch + outdoor patio. UNIT D: 3 Bedrooms, 1 Bath, brand new AC and brand new septic, new kitchen cabinets. The workshop by the Unit A is built on a foundation slab (concrete). 20 minutes to the airport, 35 min to the Capitol. Tollway 71 is coming soon. Space X/Boring Company are only 12 minutes away. Tesla Giga - 20 min.
